comments: Barnes (SAC) establishes himself in Christie's (LAL) path and does not deliver illegal contact as Christie navigates around the screen.
Holmes (SAC) moves alongside James' (LAL) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt. Holmes' hand also comes down but it avoids making contact with James' arm.
Murray (SAC) initiates contact with Gabriel's (LAL) arm, which affects his play at the basket.
Gabriel (LAL) does not pull down or hang on the rim while the ball has a chance to score during his shot attempt near the rim.
Huerter (SAC) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Holmes (SAC) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Murray's (SAC) arm is not in a legal vertical position when he initiates contact with James' (LAL) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Beverley (LAL) slightly leans into Barnes' (SAC) body and marginal contact occurs as they come together at the start of the drive.
Westbrook (LAL) brushes Barnes' (SAC) off-arm as he removes it from the ball and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Metu (SAC) legally contests James' (LAL) jump shot attempt.
Toscano-Anderson (LAL) swipes down and marginal arm contact occurs with Holmes (SAC) as they engage after the rebound.
Toscano-Anderson (LAL) raises his arm to contest and makes contact with Fox's (SAC) arm that affects his jump shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) steps forward and initiates contact with Nunn's (LAL) body, which affects his jump shot attempt.
Christie (LAL) commits a clear path foul on Holmes (SAC).
Gabriel (LAL) commits a take foul on Lyles (SAC).
